{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idb0c0565e-2930-11f1-a69d-9cbca84c43f0","identifier":"/us/usc/t37/s1012"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1012"},"text":"§ 1012.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Disbursement and accounting: pay of enlisted members of the National Guard","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amounts appropriated for the pay, under subsections (a), (b), and (d) of section 206, section 301(f), section 402(e), and ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t37/s1002"},"text":"section 1002 of this title","children":[],"tail":", of enlisted members of the Army National Guard of the United States or the Air National Guard of the United States for attending regular periods of duty and instruction shall be disbursed and accounted for by the Secretary of Defense. All such disbursements shall be made for 3-month periods for units of the Army National Guard or Air National Guard under regulations prescribed by the Secretary of Defense, and on pay rolls prepared and authenticated as prescribed in those regulations."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idb0c0565f-2930-11f1-a69d-9cbca84c43f0"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/258/s2/i/2/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–258, § 2(i)(2)(B)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1982-09-13"},"text":"Sept. 13, 1982","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/96/1061"},"text":"96 Stat. 1061","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/145/tXIII/s1303/b/13/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–145, title XIII, § 1303(b)(13)(A)","children":[],"tail":", (B), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1985-11-08"},"text":"Nov. 8, 1985","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/99/741"},"text":"99 Stat. 741","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attr